VERSATILE USES: The end of this fireplace poker tool uses the pointed hook to rake coals and turns logs to nurture the fire，These all-in-one tools can create a fire in a fireplace, campfire, woodstove, and more     FIRE POKER and BLOWPIPE IN ONE: Unscrew the tapered tip Keep clean.Firepit poker for outside pits,Portable and 2-PART ASSEMBLY Outdoor Firepit tool can be used in the patio, backyard, porch, or at the campground.The fire poker Detachable Design Makes It Easy To Pack For Camping Or Hiking.     WONDERFUL GIFT FOR FIRE LOVER - The surface of the firepit poker has an anti-rust coating and High-temperature resistance, it has not bend due to the heat. and with ergonomic wooden handle, a comfortable feel and balance to our fireplace poker.It also with a Hanging Leather Lanyard and waterproof nylon pouch.All in all, it's a fabulous gift for fire pits lovers and Solo Stove Accessories
